3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The agent-based model used in the paper can be considered a system, and the paper discusses the dynamics of the Internet, which can be seen as a system. 
4. cs.CY (Cryptography and Security) - The paper does not explicitly discuss cryptography and security, but these topics are relevant to the Internet and its growth. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) - Similar to cs.CY, the paper does not explicitly discuss cryptography and security, but these topics are relevant to the Internet and its growth.
